snippet.textDisplay:
If as the so called very “expert” doctor is correct and masks cannot prevent us from getting infected, then why keep the masks for medical personnel to use anyways?? It won’t help them too??!!

The real “story” is masks do help except that we are running out worldwide and in order to prevent panic buying and hoarding, governments and WHO are releasing the similar narrative which is don’t wear mask. However, in the very beginning, before there was the worldwide shortage of masks, they told us to wear masks!

By the way, I won’t give any credibility to what WHO says anyway. Do you guys realize that they basically have not been doing much especially in the beginning except for asking for money? Also please do google and find out more for yourself about the simulation they ran with representatives from different nations during the World Economic Forum in November last year (that’s why, just about 3 months ago), in which the scenario was exactly similar to what we are experiencing now. And yes, the same things that WHO “decided” then would be the best for us is their current narrative which is no restriction on trade and travel, global community to give money to fund WHO’s supposedly leadership role in solving this problem and private sector ie the large successful corporations to offer themselves up to support WHO’s initiatives in transport and delivery as well as supply chain support. Hmm, is WHO using this to cement their position as the leader? To obtain more power? Please remember, WHO is an arm of the UN and how better to make everyone toe the line and listen to you? - threaten their health (lives)!

In the first place, prevention is always the key. China missed the window of opportunity in the beginning (by shutting up the doctors) and now, they are suffering for it. They are also making us suffer along with them. I feel citizens of other countries should do their best to prevent infection which is stay at home (self-isolation), use a mask if you need to go out and walk fast and practice social distancing ie no shaking of hands etc. (watch contagion the movie to know more). Citizens of other countries must each do your part so that you do not get infected and host the virus whereby the virus begins to multiply. Because you see, that’s the only way the virus can multiply in your country. So don’t play host to the virus!!!

Be safe and well, everyone.

snippet.textDisplay:
In the U.S., 80,000 people died of flu, winter 2017; population of 329 million = .ooo2% of population...that's approximately 889 deaths every day, for 3 months.
Wuhan Coronavirus officially presented on 8th of December 2019 and, ONLY 800 deaths??? In a population of 1.4 BILLION (1 thousand, 400 million), that = .000003% of the population...at a rate of ONLY 6-7 deaths, per day.


Coronaviruses (7 strains) were discovered in the 1960s, and no vaccine has been successfully developed.
Novel coronavirus (2019-nCoV), also known as Wuhan coronavirus.- 800+ confirmed deaths, in 2 months.

Preliminary study providing a tentative 3% estimate for case fatality rate.
Mortality rate for SARS was 10% and for MERS 34% ...case-fatality proportion in this cohort is approximately 14.6%, and the overall case fatality proportion appears to be closer to 3%.

Importantly, in emerging viral infection outbreaks the case-fatality ratio is often OVERESTIMATED in the early stages because case detection is highly biased towards the more severe cases.
As further data on the spectrum of mild or asymptomatic infection becomes available, the case-fatality ratio is likely to DECREASE.
